  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: You look like you've been carrying too much by yourself.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Is it that obvious?
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: Only if you have had practice hiding it.
  - Speaker: Madame Lichenia
    Text: Come here. We will let the cards do some of the speaking.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Okay. Let's do it.
